=Khulafadii Umawiyiinta=
{{Template:Khulafadii Umawiyiinta}}


'''[[Khulafadii Umawiyiinta]]''' ([[ingiriis]]: Umayyad Caliphate; [[carabi]]: ﺍﻟﺨﻼﻓﺔ ﺍﻷﻣﻮﻳﺔ ama  ﺍﻷﻣﻮﻳﻮﻥ) waa waa dowladii [[Islaam]]ka ee maamulka kala wareegtay [[Afarta Khulafo]] taasi oo uu aasaasay [[Khaliifka 5aad]] ee ku xigay [[Khulafo Raashidiinta]]. Boqortooyada Dawladdani waxaa sameeyay asxaabiga weyn ee [[Mucaawiya]] wakhti ka dambeeysay dhimashaddii [[Nebi]] [[Muxamed]] (c.s.w).<ref>"([[ingiriis]]: Umayyad Caliphate; [[carabi]]: ﺍﻟﺨﻼﻓﺔ ﺍﻷﻣﻮﻳﺔ ama  ﺍﻷﻣﻮﻳﻮﻥ)"</ref> [[Boqor|Boqortooyada]] waxaa aasaasey [[Mucawiya]] (af-[[carabi]]: ﺍﻷﻣﻮﻳﻮﻥ, ama ʾUmawiyyūn, sidoo kale ﺑﻨﻮ ﺃﻣﻴﺔ, Banū ʾUmayya) taasi oo saldhig u ahayd magaalada barakeysan ee [[Makka]].<ref>"[[labaad]] ee maamuladii [[4|afarta khulafo]] [[Islaam]]ka ee la sameeyay dhimashaddii [[Nebi]] [[Muxamed]] (c.s.w)"</ref> 
Ka dib maamulkii [[Cusmaan binu Cafaan]] (644–656), waxaa hogaanka dowladii [[Islaam]]ka la wareegay [[Mucawiya|Mucawiya binu Sufyaan]] oo si xoog ah ku qabsaday maamulka isla markaana ka dhigay hogaanka Islaamiyiinta mid dhaxaltooyo ah. Mucawiya wuxuu wakhti dheer masuul ka ahaa gobolada dalka [[Suuriya]], markuu la wareegay maamulka dowladii Islaamkana wuxuu magaalo madax ka dhigtey caasimada [[Dimishiq]].<ref>"Mucawiya wuxuu wakhti dheer masuul ka ahaa gobolada dalka [[Suuriya]]"</ref> 

Si kastaba ha ahaatee, wakhtigii Umawiyiintu haysay hogaanka boqortooyadii Islaamka waxay gaadhsiiyeen dhul aad u balaadhan ayagoo qabsadey [[Afrika|waqooyiga Afrika]], dhamaan deegaanada [[Bari|Bariga dhexe]], meelo ka mid ah [[Aasiya|Aasiyada kore]] ilaa meelo badan oo [[Yurub|koonfurta Yurub]] ah sida wadanada [[Isbania|Isbayn]], [[Giriig]] iyo gasiiradaha u dhow.<ref>"[[Aasiya|Aasiyada kore]] ilaa meelo badan oo [[Yurub|koonfurta Yurub]] ah sida wadanada [[Isbania|Isbayn]], [[Giriig]]"</ref> Markey Dawladda Umawiyiintu mareysay meeshii ugu sareeysay waxay heeysatay [[dhul]] aad u balaadhan oo dhan [[milyan|5.79]] [[mayl|mayl labalaaban]] (15,000,000 km<sup>2</sup>), taasi oo ah [[boqor]]tooyadii ugu balaadhneyd ee [[duni]]du aragto iyo mida shanaad ee ugu weyn waligeed.  

